<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="obviously-adv">obviously <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'ɒbviəsli/    美 /'ɑːbviəsli/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-clearly">1.★ <strong>显而易见地 (clearly)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Obviously, the ability to talk is something that marks humans off from animals.
显然，说话的能力把人类和动物区分开来。</p><footer>2010 江西</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>Most people on this island are recreational fishers, and <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (obvious), fishing forms an actual part of their leisure time.  （2004 上海改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. obviously  </p></div>